    "body": "I actually took a look at this and fixed it... I am working to try to integrate this upstream so Geth team does not have to manage a fork of blockscout (its over 2000 commits behind). \r\n\r\nhere is my docker for intuition: https://github.com/syscoin/blockscout/blob/master/Dockerfile\r\n\r\nSyscoin has a fork of geth but we tweaked pupeth, some things that might be interesting are adding ability for those composer env variables to be parameterized by the user but for now we just hardcoded them but these allow customization of the explorer: https://github.com/sidhujag/go-ethereum/blob/nevm/cmd/puppeth/module_explorer.go#L32",
